If not me…then who?!

Another night dancing the night away spinning for @gq  @willwelch ❤️❤️

Another year around the sun 🎂🎈…

Blessed with all the love, endless laughter, piñata’s with pre rolls, sparkles, runway looks, du rags, MF DOOM, a Nick Cave inspired cake, vinyls & deep cuts 💖🔊🫶🏽 I’m loving all of it right now 🥰🥹 
*i’m a Capricorn…recovery time was real🫠*
Kicked off pre-Grammy celebration with @greygoose  sound sessions with the one and only @jazminesullivan 💖 Thanks for having me ✨
Just a baddie w/ her baddie friends 💁🏽‍♀️ Closed out Grammy week djing w/ @kaytranada @djpee.wee ❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥
Less than 24hrs in NYC celebrating NYFW with @highsnobiety x @stockx ❤️‍🔥 Loved the fits and the party vibes❤️‍🔥

A little over 6 months ago I started fucking with my drum machine again (and a bit more seriously) with the help of my sensei @beatsbyjblack because I’ve always wanted make this a part of my live sets and even though I was super hesitant to share this my friends have been on my ass and they are tired of me sending them videos 💀🥹 So here…I’m coming to terms that consistency builds skill and everything is a process so I don’t have to be perfect to share 🥹

So I picked one of my favorite songs for this cold ass rainy day in LA just in case you needed some love too 💖🫶🏽💖
In the stillness my spirit speaks the loudest ✨🌊✨

While I’m back in the studio and booked and busy IRL..Avatar Kitty is not missing a beat in the meta verse 💁🏽‍♀️ Make sure you tap in with @kittycashworld as we are gearing up to bring back Kitty’s World Season 3 ❗️

Let’s get into the beats…

1. Couture @schiaparelli for @vanityfair Oscar’s party. 
2. Cooking up the new set for Season 3. 
3. The face is givinggg
4. We love @theattico and @jumpman23 combo for a chill day 
5. Don’t play with it…Front row @versace thanks to my boo @donatella_versace 
6. Back in the stu 💖
7. Close up for your mood board 😮‍💨
8. Stay tuned 🫶🏽
A lil bit of this…a lil bit of that ❤️‍🔥
What more can I say 🍒🍒

Yerrr…When I first saw @madlib @markronson using recycled sounds to make songs from scratch I thought it was sick and couldn’t wait to put my twist on it! 

I downloaded the kits from greentoclear.com <http://greentoclear.com/> and then threw my favorite sounds into Mochi (my MPC) 💖 

It was my first time using all original sounds taken from recycling facilities. I made a few but this was my fave!

This beat was made using sounds from @thecocacolaco @sprite @seagramsgingerale @frescausa #RecycledRecords

I don’t know who needs to hear this but “stop being so hard on yourself…little by little.”

Just a freestyle I did today to calm my nerves…and remind myself…to be a little bit kinder to myself…have a bit more grace…a bit more patience. Everything is working itself out little by little and maybe someone else needed that reminder too. I’m so in love with this song “Little by Little” by @themarias 🫶🏽 it gives me a hug when I’m in my feels 🫶🏽 and wanted to share with you.

Dropped an unreleased beat with @jointhepressure x @diesel as an NFT and it flew off the virtual shelves in less than 24 hours 🥹🫶🏽😹… Thanks for supporting “Late Night Thoughts” can’t wait for the next one. 

Full interview via @kittycashworld soon 🥰💖

Now that I have your attention…
Tomorrow we are @hauserwirth celebrating the opening  for “American Gurl.” A group film exhibition curated  by @kilokish and @zehrahmed presented by @womxninwindows 🫶🏽💖🫶🏽🥰 EXTREMELY PROUD  friend post 🥹🥹 💖💖💖 see you there!!

Here’s a little taste of my favorite pieces in my home. Thank you @pieces_by_an_aesthetic_pursuit for stopping by 🫶🏽💖. 

I fell in love with the court series since I lived in Brooklyn and saw the photography series in collaboration with @karlhab. 

Years later, I love that I’m a part of Pieces @ Home. A series of vignettes showcasing people’s taste and unique take on their personal sanctuaries. 

💖💖💖 you @jennykaplan 
Captured by my the sweetest spirit @claireesparros

It’s beautiful to see history in the making. Huge congrats to @kilokish and @zehrahmed for curating a phenomenal group film exhibit @hauserwirth 🫶🏽 The line was over an hour wait and no one wanted to go home...probably because the music was just soooo good 😹. Honored to be a part of such a beautiful night. 

The show will continue through July and I can’t wait for the next one.

Back in Nola for the night. Talk to me nice!!

Finally coming down off of my high 🥹it’s always a beautiful feeling when I get those  butterflies in my tummy and my nose starts sweating before a gig. That feeling of being overwhelmed with excitement and a bit nervous because you’re not sure what to expect, but then right before I play everything dissipates because I’m  in my safest space (behind the booth) 🥹

So happy to be able to see my growth 🥹🥰 I played my first electronic music festival this Sunday @hardfest @insomniacevents on that big ass arena stage and dropping unreleased tracks and edits and  was the best feeling evvaahhhhh!! Thanks so much for rocking out with me. 

And sending extra love to some of my favorite gurlsssss that were screaming my entire set I love y’all so much 💖 @kilokish @cocoandbreezy @judnikki 💖 and thanks to my teammmm y’all killin’ 🫶🏽 @williamrobillardcole @evanhancock @tamirs

You know when you feel like you you’re finally catching up…
More studio time…opening up for Yussef Dayes…Coco &Breezy first headline LA show…gurl time…sisterly love…Haku & I…some quality me time 🥰🎀

Feeling like a Brooklyn’s girl dream to star in @jumpman23 AJ4 Red Cement campaign 🥹💕 Alongside my sis @kilokish and gang gang @black.party 

I remember saving up and running up and down Flatbush between Raggamuffin, Sneaker King, Dr.Jays, Metro, and Jimmy Jazz days before a drop telling them to hold my size 😹 13 year old me is doing back flips and adult me has always been in love with Tinker’s design of the Jordan 4. Beyond honored to be one of the chosen few celebrating 35 years of the Jordan 4s 🏆.
